497368d1-8d9e-43b9-bdea-68852c34e8cd.do_description: To make the output, you have to...take the right side section and turn it to the left rotating two times until all colored boxes start on the right.  The image will be the overlap of the two sides.
497368d1-8d9e-43b9-bdea-68852c34e8cd.grid_description: The output grid size...is equal to the size of one of the original black section.
497368d1-8d9e-43b9-bdea-68852c34e8cd.see_description: In the input, you should see...a large grid separated into two black section with a set of grey blocks in the middle.

63ffcac7-6683-4740-afef-f32cf21594ac.do_description: To make the output, you have to....use 2 different colors and go 1,2,1,3,2,1,3,2,1 with the colors
63ffcac7-6683-4740-afef-f32cf21594ac.see_description: In the input, you should see...colored squares on a black background.

6ccf3015-65d7-46a9-935a-c0753e10ee3f.do_description: To make the output, you have to...combine the colors from the left and right side of the gray column so that they overlap and place the blocks on the right side of the grid.
6ccf3015-65d7-46a9-935a-c0753e10ee3f.grid_description: The output grid size...make the width the same as one of the areas to the left or right of the column which are equal and the length from top to bottom does not change.
6ccf3015-65d7-46a9-935a-c0753e10ee3f.see_description: In the input, you should see...blocks of two different colors on a black background separated by a column of gray blocks in the middle

edf6eae3-5401-41da-bc68-495df822f8f3.do_description: To make the output, you have to...fill in the blocks as if you have folded the right side directly over the left side, taking the gray line out.. The blocks directly beside of the gray line will overlap
edf6eae3-5401-41da-bc68-495df822f8f3.grid_description: The output grid size....is the size of the left half of the grid.
edf6eae3-5401-41da-bc68-495df822f8f3.see_description: In the input, you should see...a grid that is separated by a gray line that extends vertically down the center
